# Process Creation Event

## Event ID 4688

Most Important Event

Records process creation.

Example:

```text
Process Name
Parent Process
Command Line
PID
User
```

SOC analysts use 4688 extensively.

Example:

```text
powershell.exe
```

Command line:

```text
powershell.exe -enc XXXXXXXXX
```

Strong indicator of malicious activity.

